### ============================================
### Permissions System Tests
### استخدم REST Client extension في VS Code
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@contentType = application/json

### ============================================
### الخطوة 1: تسجيل مستخدم Manager
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "manager_test",
  "email": "manager_test@test.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "manager"
}

### ============================================
### الخطوة 2: تسجيل مستخدم QA
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "qa_test",
  "email": "qa_test@test.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "qa"
}

### ============================================
### الخطوة 3: Login كـ Manager - احفظ الـ access token
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "manager_test",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ⚠️ انسخ الـ access token من الـ response وضعه في المتغير @managerToken ↓

@managerToken = YOUR_MANAGER_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### الخطوة 4: Login كـ QA - احفظ الـ access token
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "qa_test",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ⚠️ انسخ الـ access token من الـ response وضعه في المتغير @qaToken ↓

@qaToken = YOUR_QA_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### اختبارات بدون Token (يجب أن تفشل)
### ============================================

### ❌ الحالة 1: الوصول بدون Token - يجب أن يفشل
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me/

### ❌ الحالة 2: Manager-only بدون Token - يجب أن يفشل
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/manager-only/

### ❌ الحالة 3: QA-only بدون Token - يجب أن يفشل
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/qa-only/

### ============================================
### اختبارات مع Manager Token
### ============================================

### ✅ الحالة 1: /me/ مع Manager Token - يجب أن ينجح
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me/
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ✅ الحالة 2: /manager-only/ مع Manager Token - يجب أن ينجح
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/manager-only/
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ❌ الحالة 3: /qa-only/ مع Manager Token - يجب أن يفشل (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/qa-only/
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ✅ الحالة 4: /manager-or-qa/ مع Manager Token - يجب أن ينجح
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/manager-or-qa/
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### اختبارات مع QA Token
### ============================================

### ✅ الحالة 1: /me/ مع QA Token - يجب أن ينجح
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me/
Authorization: Bearer {{qaToken}}

### ❌ الحالة 2: /manager-only/ مع QA Token - يجب أن يفشل (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/manager-only/
Authorization: Bearer {{qaToken}}

### ✅ الحالة 3: /qa-only/ مع QA Token - يجب أن ينجح
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/qa-only/
Authorization: Bearer {{qaToken}}

### ✅ الحالة 4: /manager-or-qa/ مع QA Token - يجب أن ينجح
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/manager-or-qa/
Authorization: Bearer {{qaToken}}

### ============================================
### اختبارات Token غير صحيح
### ============================================

### ❌ الحالة 1: Token غير صحيح - يجب أن يفشل (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me/
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_here

### ❌ الحالة 2: Token منتهي الصلاحية - يجب أن يفشل (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me/
Authorization: Bearer expired_token_here

### ============================================
### ملاحظات:
### 1. استخدم REST Client extension في VS Code
### 2. ابدأ من الأعلى للأسفل
### 3. انسخ الـ tokens من responses وضعهما في المتغيرات
### 4. النتائج المتوقعة:
###    - بدون token: 401 Unauthorized
###    - Manager في QA-only: 403 Forbidden
###    - QA في Manager-only: 403 Forbidden
###    - مع token صحيح: 200 OK
### ============================================

